\cb5   \cf6 What is Personal User? You register the account on DeyeCloud as personal user.\cf4            \cb1 \
\cb5   \cf6 Invoke \{baseUrl\}/v1.0/account/token?appId=\{AppId\}(you obtained from creating \cf4             \cb1 \
\cb5   \cf6 application)\cf4                                                                              \cb1 \
\cb5   \cf6 Notice\cf4                                                                                    \cb1 \
\cb5   \cf6 Parameter 'appId' is put on the URL.\cf4                                                      \cb1 \
\cb5   \cf6 Field 'password' should be in SHA256 encrypted and in lowercase.\cf4                          \cb1 \
\cb5   \cf6 Multiple token calling will not invalidate the original one.\cf4                              \cb1 \
